			<div class="content" id="post-content-4327299">
									

<p>My third collab, this time with <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/laneous" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4894577); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4894577&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1565478810" alt="Laneous" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4894577)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/laneous" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4894577); return false;">Laneous</a></span>! Was a very fun, enjoyable experience all around, and I'm glad we got to humanize Parawatch as a group a bit more.</p>
<p>Image Sources: <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:XTRA%5E%5E_chupacabra_spotted_in_southern_US_-_panoramio.jpg">Chupacabra</a>, <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:KockasfuluNyul.JPG">Creepy Puppet Thing</a>, and <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Squid_komodo.jpg">Cali</a></p>
<p>Big thanks to our critters and beta readers:</p>
<ul>
